name: Bobby Lee - Ballet: World's EASIEST wallet!
tweet: Until then, we'll continue to answer every question with as much specificity and transparency as possible.  Thank you @nvk for bringing up this important topic, and I look forward to having more of these discussions with you and other experts.

name: Bobby Lee - Ballet: World's EASIEST wallet!
tweet: We're open to suggestions from security experts & other vendors, about how best to perform a comprehensive security audit of our multinational two-factor key generation & manufacturing process.   We would pay for travel and expenses for a qualified expert(s) to conduct an audit.

name: Bobby Lee - Ballet: World's EASIEST wallet!
tweet: We have yet to find an established & reputable standards organization that can conduct this type of audit, to issue a certification that is recognized by the cryptocurrency industry.  This isn‚Äôt only a challenge for us, but for every company in the industry.

name: Bobby Lee - Ballet: World's EASIEST wallet!
tweet: I ran a major exchange for 5 years (BTCChina @YourBTCC) and manufactured 22,000+ physical bitcoins at BTCC Mint (loaded with 8,700+ BTC), with no security failures.  A qualified auditor would at least need to have this kind of private key security experience as I do.

name: Bobby Lee - Ballet: World's EASIEST wallet!
tweet: We haven't had an independent security audit yet.  We're currently unaware of any qualified experts who publicly offer this service. We reached out to traditional certification entities like ISO-9000; they declined b/c they're not qualified (no experience) to evaluate our process

name: Bobby Lee - Ballet: World's EASIEST wallet!
